'''丹尼爾·保羅·巴德'''（{{lang-en|Daniel Paul Bard}}，{{bd|1985年|6月25日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於科羅拉多洛磯。他先前曾效力過波士頓紅襪。2011年，巴德曾在紅襪隊寫下連續25場出賽無失分的隊史紀錄。當時他的最快球速可來到102英里(約時速164公里)，不過接下來他罹患了投球失憶症(Yips)。2013年後，巴德便沒在大聯盟出賽。經過四個球季挑戰重返大聯盟都失敗後，巴德宣布第一次退休。2020年，巴德東山再起，並成功加入洛磯隊且睽違7年重返大聯盟。
==職業生涯==
===波士頓紅襪===
====2009年====
5月101日，紅襪隊宣布將投手[[哈維爾·洛佩茲|哈維爾·洛佩茲]]放進指定讓渡名單。巴德也從3A升上大聯盟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090510&content_id=4666492&vkey=pr_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos |title=The Official Site of The Boston Red Sox: Official Info: Red Sox select right-handed pitcher Daniel Bard to active roster |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2011-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607012914/http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20090510&content_id=4666492&vkey=pr_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月13日，巴德達成大聯盟初登板，他主投2局無失分。

5月20日，巴德首度在芬威公園亮相，不過他只投了0.2局就被換下場。他在面對費城人的比賽中拿下個人生涯首次救援成功。8月26日，他拿下了大聯盟首勝。

這年季後賽，巴德還在ESPN擔任體育播報記者。<ref>[http://sports.espn.go.com/boston/news/story?id=4535833] {{Wayback|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/boston/news/story?id=4535833 |date=20121104193737 }} Red Sox reliever Daniel Bard chronicles his playoff preparations - ESPN Boston</ref>
====2010年====
這年巴德一樣擔任球隊牛棚要角。他出賽73場比賽，送出76次三振，防禦率僅1.93。
====2011年====
這年巴德締造了連續25場比賽出賽無失分的隊史紀錄，原紀錄是由[[烏蓋特·厄比納|烏蓋特·厄比納]]所締造。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.weei.com/sports/boston/this-just-in/21122106/miller-ellsbury-help-sox-cook-os|title=Miller, Ellsbury help Sox cook O's|last=Speier|first=Alex|date=July 20, 2011|publisher=[[WEEI_(AM)|WEEI]]|accessdate=May 23, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305001202/http://m.weei.com/sports/boston/this-just-in/21122106/miller-ellsbury-help-sox-cook-os|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

不過巴德在這年球季末突然表現不佳，他在9月份拿下0勝4敗，防禦率高達10.64。該月他送出了9次保送，比他前3個月的保送數總和還高。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/boston/mlb/story/_/id/7036912/boston-red-sox-ugly-september-shows-numbers|title=Boston Red Sox ugly September shows by the numbers|last=Lundblad|first=Jeremy|date=September 29, 2011|publisher=ESPN.com|accessdate=May 23, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205019/http://espn.go.com/boston/mlb/story/_/id/7036912/boston-red-sox-ugly-september-shows-numbers|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2012年====
這年紅襪隊決定讓巴德擔任先發投手，不過他僅拿下5勝6敗，防禦率為5.24。6月5日，巴德先發1.2局，丟出2次觸身球、6次保送並掉了5分。他也隨後被下放到小聯盟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1209939-boston-red-sox-send-daniel-bard-to-minor-leagues |title=Boston Red Sox Send Daniel Bard to Minor Leagues |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2012-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609082140/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1209939-boston-red-sox-send-daniel-bard-to-minor-leagues |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在3A的表現依舊沒有起色，20.1局投球送出15次保送，防禦率高達7.08。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=bard--001dan|title=Daniel Bard Minor League Statistics & History - Baseball-Reference.com|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=July 25, 2012|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416124007/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=bard--001dan|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月30日，因為球隊釋出Zach Stewart，巴德也短暫回到大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/redsox/roster/transactions/2012/08 |title=Red Sox Roster & Staff – Transactions |website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |date=August 2012 |accessdate=March 6, 2020}}</ref>
====2013年====
該年巴德從2A開季，並在4月23日被叫上大聯盟。他在大聯盟出賽2場比賽，合計投了1局失1分。而這也是他在2010年代的最後一次大聯盟亮相。4月28日，球隊將他下放到3A，並升上Joel Hanrahan。<ref name="Bradford">{{cite web|url=http://fullcount.weei.com/sports/boston/baseball/red-sox/2013/04/28/daniel-bard-headed-back-to-minors-to-make-room-for-joel-hanrahan/|title=Daniel Bard headed back to minors to make room for Joel Hanrahan|last=Bradford|first=Rob|date=April 28, 2013|publisher=[[WEEI-FM|WEEI-FM]]|accessdate=April 28, 2013|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001134757/http://fullcount.weei.com/sports/boston/baseball/red-sox/2013/04/28/daniel-bard-headed-back-to-minors-to-make-room-for-joel-hanrahan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月1日，他遭到球隊指定讓渡。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/redsox/roster/transactions/2013/09 |title=Red Sox Roster & Staff – Transactions |website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |date=September 2013 |accessdate=March 6, 2020 |archive-date=2022-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210212507/https://www.mlb.com/redsox/roster/transactions/2013/09 }}</ref>
===芝加哥小熊===
2013年9月4日，小熊隊從讓渡名單挑走了巴德。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/chicago/mlb/story/_/id/9634346/daniel-bard-claimed-waivers-chicago-cubs|title=Daniel Bard claimed off waivers by Chicago Cubs|date=September 6, 2013|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=November 6, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173529/http://espn.go.com/chicago/mlb/story/_/id/9634346/daniel-bard-claimed-waivers-chicago-cubs|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年12月2日，巴德成為了自由球員。
===德州遊騎兵===
2014年1月31日，巴德和遊騎兵隊簽約。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://espn.go.com/dallas/mlb/story/_/id/10385179/texas-rangers-minor-league-deal-daniel-bard | title=Rangers near deal with Daniel Bard | publisher=ESPN.com | date=January 31, 2014 | accessdate=January 31, 2014 | author=Durrett, Richard | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304142141/http://espn.go.com/dallas/mlb/story/_/id/10385179/texas-rangers-minor-league-deal-daniel-bard | dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他的控球突然失準，在1A裡他僅投了0.2局，就送出了7次觸身球與9次保送。<ref>{{cite newspaper |last=Speier |first=Alex |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/sports/2016/03/14/daniel-bard-making-comeback-attempt-with-pirates/CzKgz7dEMKPI2f9VbjLBNO/story.html |title=After losing control, Daniel Bard regains it |work=The Boston Globe |date=March 14, 2016 |accessdate=June 7, 2016 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023054334/https://www.bostonglobe.com/sports/2016/03/14/daniel-bard-making-comeback-attempt-with-pirates/CzKgz7dEMKPI2f9VbjLBNO/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月19日，他遭到遊騎兵釋出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2014/06/texas-rangers-release-daniel-bard.html/ |title=Texas Rangers release Daniel Bard |work=The Dallas Morning News |first=Gerry |last=Fraley |date=June 19, 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621234417/http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2014/06/texas-rangers-release-daniel-bard.html/ |archivedate=2014-06-21 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===重返芝加哥===
2015年1月18日，巴德與小熊簽下小聯盟合約。不過該年他完全沒升上大聯盟，並在球季結束後成為自由球員。
===聖路易紅雀===
2016年1月11日，巴德以小聯盟約加入海盜隊。不過他在5月14日遭到釋出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.todaysknuckleball.com/knuckleball-news/daniel-bard-pirates/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2017-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730113723/https://www.todaysknuckleball.com/knuckleball-news/daniel-bard-pirates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月6日，他加入了紅雀隊。<ref>{{cite web |last=MCaffrey |first=Jen |url=http://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2016/06/st_louis_cardinals_sign_former.html |title=St. Louis Cardinals sign former Red Sox pitcher Daniel Bard to minor-league deal |website=MassLive.com |date=June 6, 2016 |accessdate=June 7, 2016 |archive-date=2017-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730065701/http://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2016/06/st_louis_cardinals_sign_former.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在紅雀的高階1A出賽了8場比賽，3局的投球失了8分。2017年，他在2A投了8.2局掉了10分。而他也在該年5月18日遭到球隊釋出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transactions-may-13-19/#4bfa0Z1ZFAm0bOlx.97 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2017-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109024656/http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transactions-may-13-19/#4bfa0Z1ZFAm0bOlx.97 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===紐約大都會===
2017年6月11日，巴德與大都會簽下小聯盟約。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/mets/roster/transactions/2017/06 |title=Mets Roster & Staff – Transactions |website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |date=June 2017 |access-date=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206163258/https://www.mlb.com/mets/roster/transactions/2017/06 }}</ref>他在新人聯盟出賽一場，不過他僅投了0.2局就失了4分。同年10月3日，巴德宣布第一次退休。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=453268#/career/R/pitching/2019/ALL |title=Daniel Bard – Stats, Highlights, Bio |website=MiLB.com |accessdate=March 6, 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813114808/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=453268#/career/R/pitching/2019/ALL |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年2月1日，巴德加入響尾蛇隊，成為了球員的指導老師。<ref>[http://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2018/02/daniel_bard_former_boston_red.html Daniel Bard, ex-Boston Red Sox RHP, joins Diamondbacks as player mentor; Jonny Gomes to be rookie ball hitting coach] {{Wayback|url=http://www.masslive.com/redsox/index.ssf/2018/02/daniel_bard_former_boston_red.html |date=20180709035151 }}.  Retrieved April 2, 2018.</ref>
===科羅拉多洛磯===
2020年2月，巴德宣布他要再次挑戰大聯盟。2月22日，他和洛磯隊簽下小聯盟合約。球隊在簽約後直接讓巴德進入3A球隊。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/player/daniel-bard-453268 |title=Daniel Bard Stats, Fantasy & News |website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |accessdate=March 6, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203193603/https://www.mlb.com/player/daniel-bard-453268 |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月17日，球隊宣布巴德進入40人名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/07/rockies-to-select-contracts-of-daniel-bard-matt-kemp-chris-owings.html|title=Rockies To Select Contracts Of Daniel Bard, Matt Kemp, Chris Owings|author=Jeff Todd|date=July 17, 2020|website=MLB Trade Rumors|accessdate=July 18, 2020|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031103820/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/07/rockies-to-select-contracts-of-daniel-bard-matt-kemp-chris-owings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年7月25日，巴德睽違7年多終於重返大聯盟。後援1.1局無失分，並成功拿下勝投。這也是他繼2012年5月29日後再次拿下勝投。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Harding|first=Thomas|date=July 25, 2020|title=Out 7 years with yips, pitcher wins MLB return|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/daniel-bard-earns-win-in-first-mlb-game-since-2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127095546/https://www.mlb.com/news/daniel-bard-earns-win-in-first-mlb-game-since-2013|archive-date=2020-11-27|access-date=July 26, 2020|website=MLB.com|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==個人生活==
